		<p class="comment-author" itemprop="creator" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
						<cite class="fn"><a href='http://www.d-log.info/?p=4235' rel='external nofollow' class='url fn n' itemprop="url"><span itemprop="name">D&#8217;log :: blogging since 2000 &raquo; New BM&#38;AG gallery: &#8220;the story of the city&#8221;</span></a></cite>		</p>
		<p class="comment-meta"> 
			<time class="comment-published" datetime="2008-08-26T07:03:18+00:00" title="Tuesday, August 26, 2008, 7:03 am" itemprop="commentTime"><a href="http://www.createdinbirmingham.com/2008/08/25/whats-your-big-idea-for-birmingham/#comment-31334">August 26, 2008 at 7:03 am</a></time>
					</p>
		<div class="comment-content">
			<p>[&#8230;] ideas for a future Birmingham are being gathered over at Created in Birmingham, following the recent Creative Republic meet. There&#8217;s still some confusion about how local [&#8230;]</p>
		</div><!-- .comment-content -->
