		<p class="comment-meta"> 
			<time class="comment-published" datetime="2008-08-27T13:02:14+00:00" title="Wednesday, August 27, 2008, 1:02 pm" itemprop="commentTime"><a href="http://www.createdinbirmingham.com/2008/08/25/whats-your-big-idea-for-birmingham/#comment-31548">August 27, 2008 at 1:02 pm</a></time>
